Q01 At any time in your life, have you wished you were dead or wished you could go to sleep and not wake up?
Q01a When your wishes to be dead or to go to sleep and not wake up were most severe, how often did the thoughts occur?
Q01b How long did the thoughts last?
Q01c Did you make any attempt to try to control these thoughts about wanting to die or going to sleep and not waking up, whether you were successful in controlling them or not?
Q01d How easily could you control or stop these thoughts?
Q01e Choose one of the following statements that best describes whether anyone or anything did or did not stop you from wishing you were dead or that you could fall asleep and not wake up.
Q01e_1 Did you think about things like family, religion, or fear of pain or death that might affect your wish to be dead or going to sleep and not waking up?

Q01f What sort of reasons did you have for thinking about wanting to die? Was it to end the pain or stop the way you were feeling? In other words, you could not go on living with this pain or how you were feeling? Was it to get attention
Q01f_1 When you thought about wishing to be dead or going to sleep and not waking up, did you have a reason in mind like ending your pain or getting attention or revenge?
Q02 Have you actually had any thoughts of killing yourself, at any time?
Q02a When you were feeling most suicidal, how often did you think of killing yourself?
Q02b How long did these thoughts of killing yourself last?
Q02c Did you make any attempt to try to control or stop these thoughts, whether you were successful in controlling them or not?
Q02d How easily could you control or stop thinking about killing yourself?

Q02f What sort of reasons did you have for thinking about wanting to kill yourself? Was it to end the pain or stop the way you were feeling? In other words, you could not go on living with this pain or how you were feeling? Or was it to get attention
Q02f_1 When you thought about killing yourself, did you have a reason in mind like ending your pain or getting attention or revenge?
